headline: Financial Stocks Are Way Oversold: 5 Strong Buy High-Yield Dividend Ideas
summary: Financial stocks are extremely oversold, with the XLF, the financial sector ETF, down 5.70% year-to date. This follows a period of aggressive selling that was driven by interest-rate volatility, recession fears, and lingering concerns about credit quality.
